information: Castellana de Carnes S.A. is a company that specializes in production, livestock raising and fattening, slaughtering and cutting HIGH QUALITY FRESH BEEF. The cattle has traditionally been selected for the quality of the specific meat of its breed: Naturitycla, Debuey and Ternera Castellana. Today, Castellana de Carnes is one of the main Spanish companies selling high-quality fresh beef.
